eplyTime":"2020-04-13T11:23:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c7JRmaB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc7JRmaB.jpg&h=2137119e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5gsCgJX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5gsCgJX.jpg&h=eb71100e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AzGLqCh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAzGLqCh.jpg&h=6c9007c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:36:20.000Z","msg":"收工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"310d5a10aa5d4bfb48b4d4b2f4458aec461bdaa0","tid":1970734,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T22:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZfkXkqE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZfkXkqE.jpg&h=3a8bb0a2&s={SIZE}\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"fad10516db0563f1aef3354245e4f121a76b2684","tid":1970734,"uid":50386,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:16:25.000Z","msg":"禁止4人以上聚集的「限聚令」頒佈以來，警方多次引用條例巡查「黃店」，更在8.31七個月在太子站附近截查75名市民作警告。保衞香港運動傅振中今日發起「市民自發」悼念11.13在上水中磚身亡的羅伯，其間20至30在北區大會堂外聚集，惟未有警察干預。<br />\n<br />\n該批聲稱「自發」市民聚集期間，多次有人提醒參與者獻花時要「四個四個，三個兩個都得」，惟在獻花區後不時有多於十人聚集。昨日就活動向傳媒發出採訪通知的傅振中亦一直在旁，手持手機拍攝並指指點點。<br />\n<br />\n其中一名獻花市民向傳媒聲稱大家互不認識，承認大概有數十人參與，強調獻花期間有保持距離，認為並沒違反規例。雖然一度聲稱與其他參與者互不認識，她在記者追問下又稱「我哋自己都已經商量好，唔會超過4個人，保持距離咁埋去鞠個躬，我覺得呢樣嘢無乜問題。」<br />\n<br />\n工聯會前立法會議員鄧家彪和藍絲KOL「高sir」亦到場與大媽支持者自拍，「高sir」更在悼念區前豎起手指公，身旁的大媽狀甚興奮，高呼「721係假嘅！係連（林）卓廷搞出嚟！」"}}